    "comment": "Rationale: Fig. 3: coimmunoprecipitation with PSD-95 and SAPAP, colocalization with PSD-95 in rat hippocampal neurons.\n\nNote: BEGAIN was cloned by Yeast Two-hybrid Screening using the SH3 and GK domains of PSD-95 as bait.\n\n13/4/2017 Pim\n- hotspots of PSD-95 are interpreted as synapses for this annotation.. Experimental description: BAGAIN was cloned form a rat brain yeast two-hybrid library, experiments with cultured neurons are from rat. Crude synaptosomes for immunoprecipitation were prepared from rat brains. These experiments are featured in Fig. 3\n\nLiteral form M&M\nCoimmunoprecipitation-Crude synaptosomes were prepared from\nfour rat brains.\n\nLiteral from Fiure 3 legend\nC, colocalization of BEGAIN with PSD-95/SAP90 in rat primary cultured hippocampal neurons. Rat hippocampal neurons were double-stained with the polyclonal anti-BEGAIN and monoclonal anti-PSD-95/SAP90 antibodies.",
